How it works?

{#
Printmycopy:
#}

Printmycopy is self operating public printing service where you can get printout of your files like doc, pdf, exl, jpg, png, etc or also you can get photocopy of any word file document by clicking or scan photos via mobile or any internet connected device.

  1. Upload File

    You can choose a file from your device which you want to print. Allowed Files: pdf, jpg/jpeg, png, doc/docx, xls/xlsx, ppt/pptx & txt.
  2. Select Print & Payment Option

    In the print option, you have to select color mode, quality, page range & the number of copies for your print, and you can pay with online/cash(Coin) payment modes for your print, moreover we offer Free copies
  3. Search Print Station & Get Printout

    Search your nearby print station & Enter Stn-Number & SCR-Number which will be shown on print station display screen, and your print is started!
